title: Should we commission a 1 of 1 from Fvkrender for 150K?
body:
Fvkrender is a top NFT artist in the space today: https://www.instagram.com/fvckrender/?hl=en

We can commission a 1 of 1 from him for 140K in stables and 10K in uJENNY tokens from our reserves.

The piece will have a Jenny Easter Egg like other commissioned pieces by Jenny DAO.
